{"tid":1565561,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[置頂][行動post]0913 獅子山人鏈","createTime":"2019-09-13T07:56:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T12:46:30.000Z","uid":34297,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"cc3206d351c0188d91a3ca65ddf47f48ae561cff","tid":1565561,"uid":34297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T07:56:40.000Z","msg":"地點：獅子山<br />\n<br />\n集合地點：樂富地鐵<br />\n<br />\n路線：樂富地鐵-天馬苑行人天橋-經天馬苑接獅子登山徑-回龜亭-獅子山頂。<br />\n<br />\n7:30起到時會分批上山，如自己識路，可相約朋友自行以熟悉路線上山，或者7:30跟大隊由樂富站上山<br />\n9:00-9:30眾人手牽築成人鏈，由山腳伸延至山頂，並一起亮燈！<br />\n<br />\n裝備：小背囊、水1公升以上、有足夠電力的頭燈或電筒及後備電池、手提電話、風衣或防水外套、月餅、生果及自備垃圾袋。<br />\nEquipments: backpack, water (minimum 1L), torch or headlamp with spare batteries, mobile phone, rain coat or windstopper, food and garbage bags.<br />\n<br />\nChannel<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/carryonlionrock\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fcarryonlionrock&d=mymTsZ9rb3gbearwAuc4QWo8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=218a9627\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/carryonlionrock</a><br />\n<br />\n希望各位巴絲 <br />\n出到就出 <br />\n唔得都幫手推post<br />\n利申: 唔係搞手 詳情可以睇返上面嗰tg<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.15752-9/69496525_2458374647771830_3546491200821264384_n.png?_nc_cat=109&amp;_nc_oc=AQkBWamILaIuxknRcu3bhGel2Pmd_DWZzZ6yN-z7YDB61w5RX_8xeJ1-MVapuQkr-C0&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg10-1.fna&amp;oh=82cd707c1097280c44889a5fff874dbb&amp;oe=5E03ABD1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.15752-9%2F69496525_2458374647771830_3546491200821264384_n.png%3F_nc_cat%3D109%26_nc_oc%3DAQkBWamILaIuxknRcu3bhGel2Pmd_DWZzZ6yN-z7YDB61w5RX_8xeJ1-MVapuQkr-C0%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg10-1.fna%26oh%3D82cd707c1097280c44889a5fff874dbb%26oe%3D5E03ABD1&h=d969984c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"efcd162f72f83be97b06555e66224b507f34dfc3","tid":1565561,"uid":34297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T07:57:06.000Z"